    <item>
      <title>咖啡交易商疯狂一个月内缴纳 70 亿美元保证金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/highest-coffee-prices-since-1977-leaves-traders-scrambling-for-cash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最近阿拉比卡咖啡价格上涨，导致一些知名生产商发现自己缺少现金来支持对冲，因此竞相解决财务问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/highest-coffee-prices-since-1977-leaves-traders-scrambling-for-cash</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 15:31:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>官员称阿达尼投资的斯里兰卡港口正在建设中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/work-continuing-on-adani-backed-sri-lanka-port-says-official</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当地一位高级官员表示，由阿达尼集团牵头的斯里兰卡港口扩建工程正在按计划进行，尽管在该印度企业集团高管在美国被起诉后，美国为该项目提供的 5.53 亿美元资金的命运仍不确定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/work-continuing-on-adani-backed-sri-lanka-port-says-official</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 08:41:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国以报复性金属禁令加剧美国贸易紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/china-bans-germanium-gallium-exports-to-us-in-tit-for-tat-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统拜登领导的政府加大对北京的技术限制后，中国采取针锋相对的举措，禁止进口多种高科技和军事用途的材料，此举加剧了与美国的贸易紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/china-bans-germanium-gallium-exports-to-us-in-tit-for-tat-move</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 08:21:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗原油制裁和 OPEC+ 产量协议取得进展推动油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国对伊朗原油实施更多制裁，且 OPEC+ 在阻止伊朗原油出口至市场的协议上取得进展，油价创下两周多以来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-3</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 23:36:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：标普 500 指数 11 万亿美元的涨势显露出疲态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[推动股市创下一系列历史新高的涨势已显露出疲态，投资者正在等待本周的关键就业数据和杰罗姆·鲍威尔的讲话，以寻找美联储是否会在 12 月降息的线索。债券和美元几乎没有变动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 22:37:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
